zkp-hamiltonian (1.0.0-1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Zero-Knowledge Proof implementation based on Hamiltonian Cycle
  * NIZK transformation via Fiat-Shamir heuristic
  * SHA3-256 commitments via OpenSSL
  * CLI tools: zkp-keygen, zkp-prover, zkp-verifier
  * Binary serialization for network transmission

